HEADWORD: Sorcerer
<hw>Sor"cer*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>sorcier</ets>. See <er>Sorcery</er>.]</ety> <def>A conjurer; an
enchanter; a magician.</def> <rj><au>Bacon.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p> <q>Pharaoh also called the wise men and the
<qex>sorcerers</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Ex. vii. 11.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
